Thyphon/Elecktra::

Elecktra and Thyphon, who carried Preborn,  arrived at the underwater 
tunnel that leaded to Black Fortress.  A slider (and hidden) door 
opened, letting them come in. The door closed. Now few minutes more 
and The three bots would be in Black Fortress.

>

and

> underwaters tunnels that lead to Black Fortress.
>
